{
  "stem": "22469.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What you mean?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The factory?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came to factory?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, wait a second.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we came to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Plaszow to Gross-Rosen, from Gross-Rosen to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't ask me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We came, it was autumn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was afternoon, on the day, and-- in the morning we came there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Afternoon, that where everything take out-- naked, thousand people-- snowing and raining.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Naked, a huge place-- and we were like-- like the ships, together, because-- And we was-- they should [INAUDIBLE]-- open there, open there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were looking for gold, for I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were waiting for showers, bath.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took hats, everything, everywhere-- hats, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My turn-- this was, approximately, 3 o'clock in the morning-- 12 hours in the snow and rain.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After the 12 hour, they put us, a group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- they shave us, everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Go to the shower.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A beautiful, warm shower-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And suddenly they stopped, and they start, like [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was ice-cold water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You-- you cannot run away, because everywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] After, every three people got one towel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now you can-- and after, they put us out, run, run, run, run.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "How-- maybe, I don't know, half mile, to another barracks, naked, wet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "One gave you a pull-over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One gave a shirt, and one gave us shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You [? go. ?] This was, maybe, 5 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, OK, we going to sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was a big, huge, about 700 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was at least 700.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To working center-- no central heating, wood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was hot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was wet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we are sweating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It is-- was terrible-- no food, beating.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the morning, soup.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
